posting_body: ['SECURE YOURS NOW BEFORE PRICES INCREASE ON 4/1/2022!', 'Living at Harbor Crest On The Lake Is Like Living On a Vacation Resort!!', 'We currently have 1 bedrooms available in JUNE.', 'Our 1-bedroom suites are $701.', 'The unit I have in mind for you has: a newer bathroom vanity, carpet, newer appliances, and large balcony to enjoy the sights and sounds of Lake Erie.', 'Our community featuring:', 'Brand New State-of-the-', 'Art Fitness Center', 'Sparkling Outdoor Pool', 'Heated Indoor Pool', 'Two Party Rooms', 'All New Common Area Upgrades Including Carpeting and Lighting', 'Lobby', 'NEW Laundry Facility in Each Building', 'Customer Service Office Offering Package Acceptance, Fax and Copy Machines', 'Underground Garage Parking Available', 'Near Public Transportation', 'Easy Access to Local Freeways', 'On-Site Management', 'Controlled Building Access', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Online Rental Payments and Maintenance Requests', 'Preferred Employer Program and Senior Discount Available', 'Wake up to spectacular views of gorgeous sunrises and say good night to brilliant sunsets over Lake Erie.', 'Along with an amazing list of community amenities, we also offer the added convenience of online rental payment and maintenance requests.', 'Visit Harbor Crest and we know you will agree - it is just what you are looking for!']
